fm: int nthUglyNumber(int n) {         vector<int> primes{2, 3, 5};         int m = primes.size();         vector<int> factor(primes.size(), 0), res(n, 1);         for (int i = 1; i < n; ++i) {             res[i] = INT_MAX;             for (int j = 0; j < m; ++j)                 res[i] = min(res[i], primes[j] * res[factor[j]]);             for (int j = 0; j < m; ++j)                 if (primes[j] * res[factor[j]] == res[i])                     ++factor[j];         }         return res.back();     }

fm: int missingNumber(vector<int> &nums) {         int n = nums.size();         int res = n;         for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i)             res ^= nums[i] ^ i;         return res;     }

fm: int removeElement(vector<int>& nums, int val) {         int n = 0;         for (int i = 0; i < nums.size(); ++i) {             if (nums[i] != val)                 ++n;             else {                 nums.erase(nums.begin() + i);                 --i;             }         }         return n;     }
